# EARNINGS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Mis ganancias (Rider)
GET {{baseUrl}}/earnings/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenRider}}

### Resumen de mis ganancias (Rider)
GET {{baseUrl}}/earnings/mine/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenRider}}





